{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836340/extras/SaikeyDiscord_new_english.png?t=1729912695\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836340/extras/banner_story_EN.png?t=1729912695\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Accused of espionage against their own country, the pure and noble sisters Silas and Leila Nanashiel find themselves imprisoned without a fair trial. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Leila gets sentenced to death for the alleged crime, her execution set to be carried out within merely a month. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Only her sister Silas can save her from this fate, by breaking Leila out of prison. However, in order to gather information for their escape, Silas is forced to make deals with other prisoners and obey the guards\u2019 harsh rule.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Though no matter what happens, she won\u2019t give up. With the help of other inmates, the two sisters will reunite in freedom. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836340/extras/banner_characters_EN.png?t=1729912695\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836340/extras/character_Silas_EN.gif?t=1729912695\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836340/extras/character_Leila_EN.gif?t=1729912695\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836340/extras/character_Helena_EN.gif?t=1729912695\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836340/extras/character_Sophie_EN.gif?t=1729912695\" /><img 